hiveArticle.title: Animal Photography - Elephant
hiveArticle.body:
This week theme of Photochain Photography Contest is Freedom. Now if we talk about freedom for the Elephant shown in the image below, he is just wanted to get himself freed from the chain. He just wanted himself to be untied so that he can roam around freely.

![IMG_20180616_140226.jpg](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmaoaPZY2pSdyVjj8UZ7gDdWm6A4ADbDcjyLyG8Ce6UkEt/IMG_20180616_140226.jpg)

### Camera : Nokia 6
